futari wa arukitsuzukeru

427
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:23,250
since we can never return again

428
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:23,250
ato ni wa modorenai kara

429
00:23:23,250 --> 00:23:29,300
Even now, deep within my heart,

430
00:23:23,250 --> 00:23:29,300
ima demo kono mune no oku,

431
00:23:29,300 --> 00:23:35,250
I still feel the pain of this indelible sin

432
00:23:29,300 --> 00:23:35,250
kesenai tsumi wa itamu kedo

